headline: Solventum to Report Fourth Quarter and Full Year Fiscal 2024 Earnings on February 27, 2025
summary: Solventum (NYSE: SOLV) will release its fourth quarter fiscal year 2024 financial results on Thursday, February 27, 2025, after the U.S. financial markets close. Following the release, Solventum management will host a webcast to discuss the results and fiscal year 2025 outlook. Other forward-looking and material information may also be discussed during the webcast.
